==============================================================================

This repository is a multi-module project:

  * raft-core             — pure Raft consensus state machine (zero I/O)
  * raft-transport-grpc   — gRPC implementation of the Transport interface
  * raft-storage-rocksdb  — RocksDB implementation of the Storage interface
  * raft-examples         — runnable distributed KV demo
  * raft-tests            — cross-module integration tests

==============================================================================

The raft-core module is a Java port and adaptation of:

